description: This file is a C header file defining external API function prototypes for a Udp Ping Client object within the ANSC framework. It includes license and copyright notices, module descriptions, and function declarations related to creating, removing, enrolling, and initializing the object.

methods.name: AnscUpcoCreate
methods.description: Creates an instance of the Udp Ping Client object with provided container and owner contexts.

methods.name: AnscUpcoRemove
methods.description: Removes the specified Udp Ping Client object instance.

methods.name: AnscUpcoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls the necessary sub-objects or dependencies for the Udp Ping Client object.

methods.name: AnscUpcoInitialize
methods.description: Initializes the Udp Ping Client object instance.
